        sdg15_q2_option_other: `Other / Not Applicable`,
        sdg15_q2_summary_instruction: `Select the answer that correspond to your project ... only one possible choice :`,
        sdg15_subtitle: `Protect, restore and promote sustainable use of terrestrial ecosystems, sustainably ! Sustainably manage forests, combat desertification, halt and reverse land degradation, halt biodiversity loss.`,
        sdg15_title: `SDG 15 / LIFE ON LAND`,
        sdg15_uia_action_artificialisation: `> ZERO LAND ARTIFICIALISATION IN 2050, TO FIGHT SOIL SEALING AS MUCH AS POSSIBLE :`,
        sdg15_uia_action_biotope: `> ENSURE THAT THE BIOTOPE IS NOT DEGRADED.`,
        sdg15_uia_action_invasive: `> NO INVASIVE SPECIES INTRODUCED ON SITE.`,
        sdg15_uia_action_renaturation: `- INTENSIVE VEGETALIZING / RENATURATION OF BUILDING SURFACES (GREEN TERRACES FOR TREES AND/OR GARDENING),`,
        sdg15_uia_action_replanting: `> REPLACEMENT / REPLANTING OF TREES THAT HAVE BEEN CUT.`,
        sdg15_uia_action_sprawl_dense: `- FIGHT URBAN SPRAWL : BUILD DENSE (300 units/ha or Population density: 450 inhabitants/ha, Land use ratio: 75%)`,
        sdg15_uia_action_sprawl_reno: `- FIGHT URBAN SPRAWL: RENOVATION`,
        sdg15_uia_action_sustainable_wood: `> USE OF WOOD FROM SUSTAINABLE SOURCES ONLY,`,
        sdg15_uia_action_traceability: `> NO USE OF WOOD WHOSE TRACEABILITY IS DOUBTFUL (PEFC Certification / ILLEGAL CUTTING, ...)`,
        sdg15_uia_action_water_landscaping: `> LANDSCAPING DESIGN TO MAINTAIN AND USE WATER ON SITE.`,
        sdg15_uia_action_woodlands: `> PROTECTION / CONSERVATION OF WOODLANDS ... INCLUDING ENDANGERED TREE SPECIES.`,
        sdg15_uia_criteria_label: `UIA IC SDG CRITERIA / Actions:`,
        sdg15_uia_intro: `Actions taken to protect and/or restore and promote sustainable use of terrestrial ecosystems:`,
        sdg15_un_target_15_1_label: `UN Target 15.1:`,
        sdg15_un_target_15_1_text: `By 2020 (*), ensure the conservation, restoration and sustainable use of terrestrial and inland freshwater ecosystems and their services, in particular forests, wetlands, mountains and drylands, in line with obligations under international agreements. * : Unlike most SDGs which have a target year of 2030, this indicator is set to be achieved by 2020. UN Indicator 15.1.1 is forest area as a proportion of total land area.`,
        sdg15_un_target_15_2_label: `UN Target 15.2:`,
        sdg15_un_target_15_2_text: `End deforestation and restore degraded forests : By 2020, promote the implementation of sustainable management of all types of forests, halt deforestation, restore degraded forests and substantially increase afforestation and reforestation globally. UN Indicator 15.2.1 is progress towards sustainable forest management.`,
        sdg15_un_target_15_3_label: `UN Target 15.3:`,
        sdg15_un_target_15_3_text: `End desertification and restore degraded land: By 2030, combat desertification, restore degraded land and soil, including land affected by desertification, drought and floods, and strive to achieve a land degradation-neutral world. UN Indicator 15.3.1 is the proportion of land that is degraded over total land area.`,
        sdg15_un_target_15_4_label: `UN Target 15.4:`,
        sdg15_un_target_15_4_text: `Ensure conservation of mountain ecosystems : By 2030, ensure the conservation of mountain ecosystems, including their biodiversity, in order to enhance their capacity to provide benefits that are essential for sustainable development.`,
        sdg15_un_target_15_5_label: `UN Target 15.5:`,
        sdg15_un_target_15_5_text: `Protect biodiversity and natural habitats : Take urgent and significant action to reduce the degradation of natural habitats, halt the loss of biodiversity and, by 2020, protect and prevent the extinction of threatened species.`,
        sdg15_un_target_15_8_label: `UN Target 15.8:`,
        sdg15_un_target_15_8_text: `Prevent invasive alien species on land and in water ecosystems : By 2020, introduce measures to prevent the introduction and significantly reduce the impact of invasive alien species on land and water ecosystems and control or eradicate the priority species.`,
        sdg15_un_target_15_b_label: `UN Target 15.B:`,
        sdg15_un_target_15_b_text: `Finance and incentivize sustainable forest management : Mobilize significant resources from all sources and at all levels to finance sustainable forest management and provide adequate incentives to developing countries to advance such management, including for conservation and reforestation.`,
        sdg15_un_targets_title: `UN Target & Indicators applicable in Architecture / SDG 15 :`,
        sdg16_comments_label: `COMMENT : Briefly describe the most original/main action implemented to promote peaceful and inclusive societies, provide access to justice for all and build effective, accountable and inclusive institutions at all levels.`,
        sdg16_feature_claims: `- Implement and respect procedures to establish open and transparent consensus structures to answer and provide a fair answer to all types of claims (contractors, users, neighborhood, ...) during the construction site.`,
        sdg16_feature_legal: `- Implement and respect procedures to ensure that the operation will take place within a legal / contractual framework guaranteeing rights to all parties excluding all forms of corruption at all levels.`,
        sdg16_feature_safety_home: `- Integration in the project - from the design stage - of effective protections (anti-burglary door and shutter system, ...) so that users feel safe inside their home ... when needed.`,
        sdg16_feature_safety_walk: `- Integration in the project - from the design stage - of effective elements (lighting, visibility, ...) so that the population feels safe walking around alone in the place they live ... when needed.`,
        sdg16_feature_satisfaction: `- Establish procedures for assessing client and user satisfaction throughout and/or at the end of the project (Quality Management System).`,
        sdg16_main_question_intro: `Actions to promote peaceful and inclusive societies for sustainable development, provide access to justice for all and build effective, accountable and inclusive institutions during the project ... such as :`,
        sdg16_subtitle: `Promote peaceful and inclusive societies for sustainable development, provide access to justice for all and build effective, accountable and inclusive institutions at all levels !`,
        sdg16_summary_instruction: `Select the answer that correspond to your project ... only one possible choice :`,
        sdg16_summary_option_0: `No specific measure taken to promote peaceful and inclusive societies and institutions ...`,
