        sdg17_feature_reporting: `> Project environmental data were measured and reported - at the national (or regional) level - to develop progress on sustainable development.`,
        sdg17_feature_sharing: `- The operation gave rise to initiatives to share data and knowledge (publications, conferences, ...).`,
